                    <p>
                        Our Deluxe king size room has a seating area, ample storage, 
                        digital safe and mini fridge. This room can also be configured with an extra roll-away 
                        bed for families of 3.</p>
                </div>
    
                <div class="price">
                    <span class="label"><strong>Price:</strong></span>
                    <p>K350</p>
                </div>
    
                <div class="room-number">
                    <span class="label"><strong>Room Number:</strong></span>
                    <p>54</p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-grids">
                    <div class="wrap">
